Bugs --------------------
- output should be Cout, otherwise it will crash
- after changing Properties you can not recompile shader to first state or reset it
- you should load a shader from cmdline, can not copy new shader and run
- osltoy window will not open in the middle of screen
- widgets are not resizable
- open menu does not work
- can not close tabs
- can not open different shaders and work on them simoultaniously
- can not update current open file if we change it outside of the app

Features ----------------
- need a place to define include path to search other osl functions (for each tab)
- each shader detect other tabs
- editor color highlight
- .clang-format detection
- preferences
- slider values are more handy (houdini style value change)
